oadInfo.ZIP</a> (Zipped 5.25-inch ProDOS disk image,
    12575 bytes)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Requirements:  Apple IIGS with System 6.0.1 or System 5.0.4 (may also =
work
   with other system software versions, but that hasn't been tested) and
